instructions: Put the plate on the charger
put the napkin on the plate vertically
put the dinner fork to the left of the plate
put the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork
put the dinner knife to the right of the charger
put the tea spoon to the right of the dinner knife
put the soup spoon to the right of the dinner spoon
put the water glass above the dinner knife
put the wine glass to the right of the water glass
put the second wine glass above the soup spoon
put the coffee cup to the right of the second wine glass
put the bread plate above the forks
put the butter knife on the bread plate
put the dessert fork to the right of the bread plate
put the desert spoon above the charger under the desert fork
